  <body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Missedit.tv</h1>
    <p>MissedIt.tv is the quickest and easiest way to find <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Magnet_URI_scheme">magnet links</a> to the stuff you want now. When possible, MissedIt.tv tries to find high-definition (720p) versions of content, and will fall back to standard-definition (480p). As always, you shouldn't trust <i>any</i> website with links to potentially-unknown software, so for an added layer of caution the exact name of the content is listed.</p>
    <p>In order for these links to do anything, you will need a <a href="http://www.bittorrent.com/">BitTorrent client.</a> Be aware you're downloading files to your computer, so exercise proper caution.</p>
    <div class="list">
    <% settings.shows.each do |x| %>
	<a href="<%= x[:magnet_link] %>"><%= x[:title] + " S" + x[:season] + "E" + x[:number]%></a><br>
	<% end %>
	</div>
  </div>

